36:19.916 --> 36:23.067
A lot of things... a lot of
reasons that... that can happen.

36:23.091 --> 36:25.349
So...

36:25.507 --> 36:27.375
So I can... I can help.

36:27.399 --> 36:29.681
Scott, step outside with me for a sec?

36:29.705 --> 36:31.859
Come on.

36:42.805 --> 36:44.412
It's okay, son.

36:45.618 --> 36:48.544
I'm right here. I'm...
I'm not going anywhere.

36:51.306 --> 36:54.102
Gotta say, not like I
didn't respect you before,

36:54.126 --> 36:55.282
because clearly I did,

36:55.306 --> 36:57.460
but after riding along with you tonight,

36:57.484 --> 36:59.605
I must say, you are something special.

37:00.970 --> 37:02.705
Not so bad yourself.

37:02.729 --> 37:04.239
Wait.

37:04.779 --> 37:06.206
Uh-oh. What's wrong?

37:11.323 --> 37:13.697
God, it's just that damn Nemo.

37:13.721 --> 37:15.553
You know?

37:15.577 --> 37:17.038
Gets me every time.

37:17.062 --> 37:18.475
Yeah, I get that, actually.

37:18.499 --> 37:21.648
- See? You and me both.
- Mm.

37:24.918 --> 37:26.612
Hey, Tee. You done changing?

37:26.636 --> 37:28.146
Yep. Just, uh...

37:29.286 --> 37:30.377
Tough surgery.

37:30.402 --> 37:31.719
- Yeah, I can imagine.
- Yeah.

37:31.743 --> 37:34.154
Hey, thank you for trusting Scott.

37:34.178 --> 37:36.331
Oh, I didn't... I didn't
trust Scott. I trusted you.

37:36.355 --> 37:38.186
Well, thank you for trusting me.

37:38.210 --> 37:39.914
I'll always trust you, you know,

37:39.938 --> 37:41.577
'cause I know you're trying to trust me.

37:41.601 --> 37:43.695
- I do trust you.
- Yeah?

37:43.719 --> 37:46.106
- Yeah.
- Yeah? You sure?

37:46.130 --> 37:48.130
Look, uh, I love you,

37:48.154 --> 37:50.018
and I love the baby, and...

37:50.042 --> 37:52.606
I'm just still struggling a little bit.

37:52.630 --> 37:53.882
You know? With... with... uh, I-I thought

37:53.906 --> 37:56.318
all this P.T.S.D. was
going away, and it hasn't.

37:56.343 --> 37:58.440
That sounds like progress to me.

38:00.532 --> 38:01.946
Look...

38:03.091 --> 38:05.116
For the record,

38:05.140 --> 38:07.985
the risks that you take, they scare me.

38:08.010 --> 38:10.260
But I <i> do</i> trust you.

38:10.284 --> 38:12.324
All right? It doesn't mean that I don't...

38:12.626 --> 38:14.549
Wanna smack you every once in a while.

38:14.573 --> 38:16.942
Hey, how did you not smack me all the time?

38:16.966 --> 38:18.204
- No, I did.
- Mm-hmm.

38:18.228 --> 38:21.090
- Mm-hmm.
- Look, when I figure this all out,

38:21.114 --> 38:22.528
it'll be good for you and me and the baby.

38:22.552 --> 38:24.705
The three of us. Promise.

38:24.730 --> 38:26.594
I know.

38:27.646 --> 38:29.376
- All right.
- All right.

38:29.400 --> 38:31.131
- I'll see you outside.
- Yep.

38:52.453 --> 38:54.384
- Hey.
- Hey.

38:54.409 --> 38:58.271
His M.R.I... what did it
show? Was it the surgery?

38:58.296 --> 39:00.994
No, it wasn't. Don't do this to yourself.

39:01.018 --> 39:04.136
When he coded, the upper
part of his spinal cord died.

39:04.160 --> 39:06.199
There was nothing you
or anybody could've done.

39:07.559 --> 39:09.268
You saved the boy's life, Scott.

39:09.292 --> 39:11.406
How can you say that?

39:11.713 --> 39:14.587
I changed his life forever.

39:15.416 --> 39:16.902
Forever.

39:18.472 --> 39:20.060
He's going
to be paralyzed, Topher.

39:20.084 --> 39:21.820
I know. I know. I know.

39:29.164 --> 39:30.481
I know.

39:30.505 --> 39:32.810
So how can I possibly make this right?

39:34.322 --> 39:36.569
How can I make this up to him?

39:36.593 --> 39:38.458
You're gonna figure out a way.

39:40.885 --> 39:42.169
I promise you.

39:42.755 --> 39:44.361
Right now, you need some rest.

39:44.385 --> 39:45.826
Let me drive you home.

39:45.850 --> 39:48.139
All right, brother.

